tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE transaction_records (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    customer_id INT NOT NULL,
    amount DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    status VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    product_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);
